#: ../../deployment/voxcpm_cpp.rst:11 ccd41bad187843e99b5da1dd4419b41b
msgid ""
"It provides a CLI tool (``voxcpm_tts``) for offline synthesis and an OpenAI-"
"compatible HTTP server (``voxcpm-server``) with streaming support."
